        dwc:species                   "vianai" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4612325>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 17. Characteristics of spermiogenesis of Neotrops waorani. A: The posterior portion of AV is already deeply sunken into the anterior pole of the nucleus in early spermatids, the subacrosomal space is widened. B: The AV is surrounded by distinct electron-dense material. C: The chromatin appears fibrillar and shows dense streaks. D: The proximal centriole is enlarged. E: The base of the axoneme is surrounded by electron-dense secretions that arrange in plates. F: The NC runs in the periphery of the nucleus appears stalked because of the irregular chromatin-condensation pattern. G: At the end of spermiogenesis, a distinct electron-dense vesicular area is formed, while the main cell components coil within the cell." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4612325/files/figure.png" .

